ext-base md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"然而，48隊新制也引發了一些討論。批評者認為過多的參賽隊伍可能影響比賽品質，且小組賽的強度差距可能拉大。但支持者則表示，擴編讓更多足球發展中國家獲得在世界最高舞台亮相的機會。\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-5 text-base md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"國際足總（FIFA）主席表示：「世界盃是屬於全世界的盛事，48隊新制讓更多國家能夠參與，這是足球全球化的重大一步。」\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-5 text-base md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"隨著小組賽的進行，新賽制的優缺點將逐漸顯現，而各隊也將在全新的競爭格局中爭取最終的榮耀。\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium transition-colors\",\"children\":\"← 返回首頁\"}]}]]}]]}],null,[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$4\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@5\"}]}]]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":null,\"buildId\":\"t62DCvP_yvtbz2daRlv9h\"}\n5:null\n","/news/$d$id":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[39756,[\"/_next/static/chunks/3xl19b9vg2cbe.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\"],\"default\"]\n3:I[37457,[\"/_next/static/chunks/3xl19b9vg2cbe.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\"],\"default\"]\n4:[]\n0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{}]}]]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":\"$W4\",\"buildId\":\"t62DCvP_yvtbz2daRlv9h\"}\n","/news":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[39756,[\"/_next/static/chunks/3xl19b9vg2cbe.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\"],\"default\"]\n3:I[37457,[\"/_next/static/chunks/3xl19b9vg2cbe.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\"],\"default\"]\n4:[]\n0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{}]}]]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":\"$W4\",\"buildId\":\"t62DCvP_yvtbz2daRlv9h\"}\n","/_index":"